trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"> </xref> egenskapen (og verdien) av en utskrift maskinvare eller programvare systemkomponent.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"> </xref> klasse for den angitte egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintProcessor> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` bør fullt nøyaktig lik navnet på en bestemt <xref:System.Printing.PrintProcessor>-egenskapen for et trykt systemobjekt, inkludert små og.</xref:System.Printing.PrintProcessor>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePrintProcessor%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueuePrintProcessor", not "PrintProcessor" or "Queueprintprocessor".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePrintProcessor%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektet må være stavet "QueuePrintProcessor", ikke "PrintProcessor" eller "Queueprintprocessor".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePrintProcessor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"> </xref> klasse som ikke har den angitte verdien for den angitte egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintProcessor> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` bør fullt nøyaktig lik navnet på en bestemt <xref:System.Printing.PrintProcessor>-egenskapen for et trykt systemobjekt, inkludert små og.</xref:System.Printing.PrintProcessor>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePrintProcessor%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueuePrintProcessor", not "PrintProcessor" or "Queueprintprocessor".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePrintProcessor%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektet må være stavet "QueuePrintProcessor", ikke "PrintProcessor" eller "Queueprintprocessor".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePrintProcessor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"> </xref> egenskapen som det <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"> </xref> representerer.

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for egenskapen som det <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"> </xref> representerer.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdien for egenskapen som det <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProcessorProperty"> </xref> representerer.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that can be cast to a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"></xref>.
